            "title": "港股午後開市30分鐘過後升穿28000點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後持續向上，恒生指數於下午約1時30分過後升穿28000點關口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至下午約1時45分，恒指報28046點，升219點或0.79%；稍早前最高見28056點，升229點。恒生科技指數跑輸，暫跌0.53%，報5869點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金融股領漲大市，友邦(01299)升約2.6%，報91.2元；中國平安(02318)漲約3.7%。油股持續揚升，中海油(00883)與中國石油(00857)均漲超過3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內房股強勢，3隻藍籌內房龍湖(00960)、華潤置地(01109)與中國海外(00688)暫均升逾4%。</p>\n</div>",
